#: index.docbook:38
msgid ""
"&kicker; is the &kde; application starter panel and is also capable of some "
"useful applets and extensions. It usually resides on the bottom of the "
"desktop."
msgstr ""
"&kicker; est le tableau de bord lanceur d'applications de &kde; et il "
"comprend aussi des extensions et des applets bien utiles. On le trouve "
"généralement en bas du bureau."

